An 18-year-old girl was at the weekend found dead in a hotel in Delta State. Her body was discovered inside the hotel in Owa Community, Ika North Local Government Area. The deceased was identified as Ogochukwu. She and two suspected internet fraudsters reportedly lodged at the hotel located along Efeizomor road. But the duo left her when they checked out. Police Public Relation Officer (PPRO), DSP Onome Onovwakpoyeya, confirmed the incident to The Nation. “I got across to the DPO Agbor and he said that a lot of things happened around the community. An investigation has commenced”, he said.